### QuantityMeasurement API - Complete Test Suite
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/quantity

# ============================================================
# 🔹 COMPARE
# ============================================================

### Compare - 1 FEET == 12 INCHES (should be EQUAL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thisQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 1.0,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  },
  "thatQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 12.0,
    "unit": "INCHES",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  }
}

<> 2026-03-24T170122.200.json

###

### Compare - 1 FEET vs 6 INCHES (should NOT be equal)
# @no-cookie-jar
POST {{baseUrl}}/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thisQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 1.0,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  },
  "thatQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 6.0,
    "unit": "INCHES",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  }
}

<> 2026-03-24T170123.200.json

###

