### Compare - EDGE CASE: null value (should throw error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thisQuantityDTO": {
    "value": null,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  },
  "thatQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 12.0,
    "unit": "INCHES",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  }
}

<> 2026-03-24T170123-1.400.json

###

### Compare - EDGE CASE: mismatched types (LengthUnit vs WeightUnit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thisQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 1.0,
    "unit": "FEET",
    "measurementType": "LengthUnit"
  },
  "thatQuantityDTO": {
    "value": 1000.0,
    "unit": "GRAM",
